\id 3JN - ZARAMO Bible Version 
\h 3YOHANA 
\toc1 LUPWILILI LWA IKADATU LWANDIKIGWE NA MTUMIGWA WA KILISTO YOHANA 
\toc2 3YOHANA 
\toc3 3Yoh. 
\mt2 LUPWILILI LWA IKADATU LWANDIKIGWE NA MTUMIGWA WA KILISTO 
\mt1 YOHANA 
\imt1 ULONGOZI 
\ip Lupwilili lwa ikadatu lwa Yohana lwandikigwa na mtumigwa wa Kilisto Yohana mmilao ya 90 songela kuvumbuka kwa Kilisto. Yohana haitambule mwenyego kamba heyo iyo yandike ulupwilili, ila koikema heyo m'vyele (1:1). Kotenda kamba viyatendile mulupwilili lwa Yohana wa ikabili (2Yoh. 1:1). Yokoneka kamba Yohana kandika Usenga Unogile wa Yohana na zimhwilili ndatu za 1Yohana, 2Yohana, na 3Yohana kipigiti viyakalile yokala Efeso. 
\ip Yohana kamwandikila lupwilili luno munhu yamtogole Kilisto yokemigwa Gayo. Kamtambula Gayo kamba mbwigaake na kumulongela yawe mwende ha wanhu wamtogole Kilisto awo wobita kubitila muisi yookala heyo. 
\iot Gali Mgati ya Ikitabu 
\io1 1. Yohana kolutambuza lupwilili lwake (\ior 1:1\ior*). 
\io1 2. Yohana komgangamiza Gayo na kumulongela kamba yawe mwende ha wanhu wamtogole Kilisto (\ior 1:2-8\ior*). 
\io1 3. Abaho kowalonga wanhu wabili wayagwe, Diotilefe na Demetilio (\ior 1:9-12\ior*). 
\io1 4. Hakimambukizo, komambukizila lupwilili lwake (\ior 1:13-14\ior*). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Lupwilili luno lolawa ha Yohana, m'vyele.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Hano \fk m'vyele \ft nhegulo yake \fqa mkulu mdidale da wanhu wamtogole Kilisto.\f* 
\p Nomwandikila Gayo, mbwigaangu inimnogele kwelikweli. 
\p  
\v 2 Mbwigaangu, nokutambikila giladi uwe na ugima mulukuli na mbuli zose zigendelele vinogile kumwako, hata na loho yako igendelele vinogile.  
\v 3 Nideng'ha ng'hani ahaja wanhu wamtogole Kilisto viwezile na kunongela vija vuulibule uzenzeleganye muikweli na vija vuugendelela kutembela muikweli.  
\v 4 Haduhu kinhu kinideng'heza ng'hani kubanza kino, kuhulika kamba wanangu wotembela muikweli. 
\s1 Gayo Kotogoligwa 
\p  
\v 5 Mbwigaangu, gweye kwabule uzenzeleganye mmbuli zose zuuwatendela wanhu wamtogole Kilisto, hata kamba hewo wahenza kumwako.  
\v 6 Wasimulila noge jako haulongozi wa wanhu wamtogole Kilisto, motenda vinogile ng'hani kamba muhawasangila giladi wagendelele na mwanza wao mnzila imnogele Mulungu.  
\v 7 Kwavija wasonga mwanza wao sama ya twaga da Kilisto na hawatogole kubokela msango wowose kulawa ha Wamhazi.  
\v 8 Avo tolondigwa kuwataza wanhu kamba wano giladi tuilumbe hamoja msang'hano yao ya kuipeta kweli. 
\s1 Diotilefe na Demetilio 
\p  
\v 9 Niwandikila wanhu wamtogole Kilisto mbuli ino, ila Diotilefe, ayo yanogelagwa kuitenda kilangizi, hautogole udaho utulinao.  
\v 10 Avo niheza nowalongela gaja goyotenda, vija voyokweneza mbuli za uvwizi yotulonga tweye. Sio higo tu, ila vivija kolema kuwabokela wanhu wamtogole Kilisto na hata kuwagomesa waja walonda kuwabokela na kuwawinga walawe mumting'hano wa wanhu wamtogole Kilisto. 
\p  
\v 11 Mbwigaangu, sambiwige gehile ila wige gaja ganogile. Munhu yoyose yotenda ganogile kalawa ha Mulungu, na munhu yoyose yotenda gehile hamonile Mulungu. 
\p  
\v 12 Kila munhu komulonga vinogile Demetilio, na kweli yenyego vivo imulonga, na tweye vivija tolava usindila sama yake, na gweye kuvitanga kamba usindila wetu kweli. 
\s1 Ndamsa za Kimambukizo 
\p  
\v 13 Nnago bwando ga kuwandikileni, ila silonda kuwandikileni na wino na peni.  
\v 14 Kipigiti kidodo hamwande notamanila kuiting'hana namwe tulongelele kihanga kwa kihanga. 
\p  
\v 15 Tindiwalo dikale namwe. 
\p Wambwiga zako wose wokulamsa. Walamse wambwiga zetu wose, mkuwatambula matwaga.